    p In this process we deployed prototype iOS apps as well as a fully working Android and iOS remote control for the TV service. Building this platform I directly recruited and managed 8 fulltime software developers.  I lead the design and implementation of multiple responsive single page web applications, iOS and Android touch interfaces, and several proprietary set top box platforms.
