    p As a software developer, I specialize in front end scripted languages, object oriented programming models, and building scalable single page web applications that conform to todays modern web standards.  Beyond building highly dynamic user interfaces, working with advanced web typography, and 2-way data binding, I also have a strong specialization in handling HD video, images, and metadata cross platform in global multi-language environments.
